Section.Label: Statement

Child.Label: Content
Child.Text:
The OSMS system was used to position the patient immediately prior to treatment and to track the patient during treatment in 3D mode. The patient was monitored for 712.74 Seconds.
The following parameters are the couch shifts which were computed by OSMS in the treatment position, in order to assess the accuracy of patient set-up and to prevent geographical miss with the radiation beam, in standard couch coordinates.
